image1304×441 32 KB  Bro, sorry to be the bearer of bad news, but if you say you withdrew from Coinbase, the last withdrawal from Coinbase to that wallet is the one that happened. Unfortunately the funds were lost, But it’s not all bad, I personally check many times where I send before I deposit it, this is what I do in my security process.
